metadata.name: Kaytranada, Montreal (Metropolis) | 19/05/2016
metadata.description:
This montage is made of shots taken at Kaytranada's sold out show in Montreal after releasing his acclaimed debut LP 99.9%.   

This album and the 99.9% tour established Kaytranada in the music industry as a recognized producer and landed him a major record deal with RCA records. 

The 99.9% tour and album made all the more impressive given the diversity of samples, guests and timeless hit tracks like “Glowed Up” and “Got it Good”

(Photography and Design by Sean Vadaru)
